---
title: Honey-Glazed Halloumi & Caesar-Style Salad with Dijon Dressing, Almonds & Feta
description: You can put down that supermarket salad because we have one that will truly blow you away with sweetly glazed halloumi and toasted almonds sprinkled on top. The croutons add a golden crunch while the Dijon mayo dressing wraps everything up with a tasty bow.

